headline: A Little Help on the Diamond
abstract: Kate Henjum and Bill Jaffee are, as he says, “a positive blip on the political radar.”
lead_paragraph: Kate Hannah Henjum and Bill Gephart Jaffee were married Jan. 18 at the Minikahda Club in Minneapolis. Kate White, an aunt of the groom who became a Universal Life minister for the event, officiated.
